reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Okay, funny story about this lamp. I bought one because the nightstand lamp I had broke, and this one looked pretty awesome. Bought it, set it up. My son saw it and wanted one. I bought it for him. Then my daughter saw it and wanted one, so I bought it for her too. Needing a lamp in a pinch created 3 very happy customers! HahaThe instructions are very easy, the lamp is sleek and small, but bright. Fits perfectly on my nightstand and doesn't take up much room. I have used it on all settings. I have a chronic condition that causes frequent stomach aches, and I sleep better with a dim light when not feeling well. The nightlight is perfect for it. My favorite is the RGB. It fades between the colors, and it makes a nice little light show that isn't to much. Brightest setting for writing or sorting things in my room. It's incredibly versatile, and I'm tempted to replace ALL of my lamps with this one! Of course, it's also handy that it's a touch lamp. I don't need to find the switch on it. Just tap, and it's on. Awesome lamp, highly recommend!!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent lamp that replaced my old bulky lamp
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Versatile RGB Touch Lamp, and I must say, it has exceeded all my expectations. This lamp is an absolute game-changer when it comes to lighting and ambiance in my home. Here's why I love it:First and foremost, the RGB feature is a true showstopper. I can easily adjust the lamp's color to match my mood or the occasion. Whether I want a calming blue, a vibrant red, or any color in between, this lamp has it all. The gentle, flicker-free light it emits creates a cozy and inviting atmosphere that instantly transforms any room.The three different brightness modes are incredibly convenient. With just one tap, I can switch between low, medium, and high brightness settings to suit various activities. Whether I'm reading a book, preparing for a good night's sleep, or simply relaxing, this lamp has the perfect lighting option for every situation.The touch control sensor on the top of the lamp is a brilliant addition. It makes turning the lamp on and off a breeze, eliminating the need for fumbling with switches or cords. Plus, the sleek and modern design of the lamp, with its smooth white lamp shade, adds a touch of elegance to any room.I also appreciate the durability of this lamp. The anti-slip pad on the base keeps it steady on any surface, and I can tell that it's built to last. The fact that it won't fade over time is a testament to its quality and longevity.One of the best things about this lamp is its versatility. It's not just a bedside lamp; it's a multi-use smart lamp that can elevate the ambiance of any space. Whether I use it as a nightstand lamp, in the baby nursery, as a reading light, or to set a romantic atmosphere, it always delivers.Lastly, I have to mention that this lamp makes for an excellent gift. Its aesthetic design and practicality make it a perfect present for friends, colleagues, adults, kids, and families alike. I can confidently say that this lamp has improved the quality of my life, and I can't recommend it enough. It's a must-have addition to any home or office decor.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to use. Works great. Clever design.
reviews.reviewText: This review is for the rechargeable lamp. Some reviewers have complained that the lamp will not change intensity-brightness on red, green, orange, etc. colors. It's not designed or made to do that. The light only changes brightness in the first mode. The white mode. Single tap starts white light mode. In white light mode, a quick short tap will change the light intensity from low, medium and high and off as you tap the top. If it is in white light mode, a 3 second press begins the multi color mode. This is the second mode. It is not designed to change brightness when in the multi color mode and it will not do that. Maybe the instructions are not clear, but their video is. That said, I use it for a bedside lamp. It is so easy to use. Short tap, white light, 3 second tap multicolor light. To exit multi color, hold down the button for three seconds and it exits multicolor mode.The lamp also has an interesting night light mode. Light must be off. Hold down the top for a long press, about three seconds. A very low intensity light turns on, likely night light mode. This thing is awesome. Will it last? I don't know. If it breaks, I will edit my review.Note: There is no charging brick in the package. The USB A to USB C cable is included. You will need to charge it via computer or cellphone charger.
